<p>Dave and John blast off on Sunday morning with a few quick tips and answers, including changing the Finder&#39;s default search (to what it&nbsp;<em>should</em>&nbsp;be), setting your Mac&#39;s default display, correcting drifting time, and more. Then It&#39;s a few questions about automating iTunes and dealing with overlapping WiFi channels. Good, geeky fun for you!</p>
